snippet.title: Astra - Official Behind the Scenes Overview Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Astra is a mixed-reality experiential game developed by Atlas V and Albyon. Players will follow the research of their late astrobiologist mother to travel in space and explore planets, dark moons, and more in the search for life. Astra is available now for Meta Quest.
